data.description: Call quickly on this spacious ranch home that has a lot to offer. Property features a nice size living room, a large kitchen with plenty of cabinets, a dining area, 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a laundry area. Property has a basement that walkouts through the garage. The basement offers a bedroom, a full bath and a family room. Call today for a showing. This property is HUD-owned Case # 201647245 and is being Sold ''AS-IS.''. FHA Insured status: Insured. Choose FHA financing to qualify for $100 down. Ask Agent for details. $100 down & 203K eligible. *FHA Insurability is subject to the buyer's appraisal.* Equal housing opportunity.
